OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777446312
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'talented and
OL,4,Ccreative' woman as drivers jailed over
OL,5,Cher death
OL,7,FA family has paid tribute to a 'deeply
OL,8,Floved' woman who died in a crash three
OL,9,Fyears ago.
OL,11,FElla Cook died in a collision that
OL,12,Fhappened on the A46 in Claverton on 15
OL,13,FApril 2023.
OL,15,FTwo men, Alfie Cook (no relation to
OL,16,FElla) and Lewis Glasby, were jailed
OL,17,Fearlier this month after the court was
OL,18,Ftold they had been racing one another
OL,19,Fbefore the collision.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777446312
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'talented and
OL,4,Ccreative' woman as drivers jailed over
OL,5,Cher death
OL,7,FGlasby, 23 of The Beeches in
OL,8,FWarminster, and Cook, 22 of Brook
OL,9,FStreet in Warminster, pleaded guilty
OL,10,Fto causing death by dangerous driving
OL,11,Fand two counts of causing serious
OL,12,Finjury by dangerous driving.
OL,14,FCook received a prison sentence of
OL,15,Fnine years and four months at Bristol
OL,16,FCrown Court on Friday 10 April. Glasby
OL,17,Freceived a prison sentence of nine
OL,18,Fyears.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777446312
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'talented and
OL,4,Ccreative' woman as drivers jailed over
OL,5,Cher death
OL,7,FBoth men will be disqualified from
OL,8,Fdriving for five years upon their
OL,9,Frelease from prison and will need to
OL,10,Fpass an extended test before regaining
OL,11,Ftheir licence.
OL,13,FElla, who lived in Warminster, was 26
OL,14,Fyears old when she died and was
OL,15,Fengaged to Kai Poa-Tams.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777446312
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'talented and
OL,4,Ccreative' woman as drivers jailed over
OL,5,Cher death
OL,7,FOn behalf of Ella's family, Kai said:
OL,8,F"It has been incredibly difficult to
OL,9,Ffind words for Ella, because the love
OL,10,FI feel for her, and the love her
OL,11,Ffamily and friends feel, is far
OL,12,Fgreater than anything words can hold.
OL,14,F"Ella was a deeply loving partner,
OL,15,Fdaughter, sister and friend. She gave
OL,16,Fherself completely to the people she
OL,17,Fcared about, always putting others
OL,18,Ffirst with a warmth that made everyone
OL,19,Ffeel safe, valued and understood.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777446312
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'talented and
OL,4,Ccreative' woman as drivers jailed over
OL,5,Cher death
OL,7,F"She had a natural way of bringing
OL,8,Fpeople together, and her kindness left
OL,9,Fa lasting mark on everyone lucky
OL,10,Fenough to know her.
OL,12,F"She was also immensely talented and
OL,13,Fcreative, with an artistic spirit that
OL,14,Fshowed in so many parts of her life.
OL,16,F"Whether through the way she expressed
OL,17,Fherself or the little touches she
OL,18,Fbrought into everyday moments, Ella
OL,19,Fmade the world around her brighter,
OL,20,Fmore thoughtful, and more beautiful.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777446312
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'talented and
OL,4,Ccreative' woman as drivers jailed over
OL,5,Cher death
OL,7,F"Alongside this, she had a wicked
OL,8,Fsense of humour, playful, quick, and
OL,9,Fsometimes perfectly silly, that filled
OL,10,Four days with tummy-aching laughter."
OL,12,FKai added: "Ella was also a valued and
OL,13,Fdedicated member of staff at NHS Blood
OL,14,Fand Transplant, progressing through
OL,15,Fher career with remarkable
OL,16,Fdetermination.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@eO]tD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777446312
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'talented and
OL,4,Ccreative' woman as drivers jailed over
OL,5,Cher death
OL,7,F"In a way that feels both
OL,8,Fheartbreaking and extraordinary, her
OL,9,Fwork came full circle, she received
OL,10,Fdonated blood after the collision,
OL,11,Fblood that she herself had helped
OL,12,Fprocess earlier that very day.
OL,14,F"We were going to get married, to
OL,15,Fbuild a home, and to raise children of
OL,16,Four own. We dreamed of sharing time
OL,17,Fwith her parents, and with her brother
OL,18,Fand sisters' children, creating a life
OL,19,Ffull of closeness and joy.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777446312
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'talented and
OL,4,Ccreative' woman as drivers jailed over
OL,5,Cher death
OL,7,F"Our children would have been the
OL,8,Fluckiest in the world to have Ella as
OL,9,Ftheir parent, because she would have
OL,10,Fgiven them the same boundless love she
OL,11,Fgave to me.
OL,13,F"Ella was truly one of a kind. She was
OL,14,Fwarm, loving, creative, and full of
OL,15,Flife`and the world feels immeasurably
OL,16,Femptier without her."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777446312
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'talented and
OL,4,Ccreative' woman as drivers jailed over
OL,5,Cher death
OL,7,FDesignated Investigating Officer, Emma
OL,8,FLing, said: "Both Alfie Cook and Lewis
OL,9,FGlasby were driving well in excess of
OL,10,Fthe speed limit before the fatal
OL,11,Fcollision occurred.
OL,13,F"Excessive speed is one of the Fatal
OL,14,FFive causes that lead to most death
OL,15,Fand serious injury collisions in this
OL,16,Fcountry. Both men deliberately ignored
OL,17,Fthe speed limits and drove dangerously
OL,18,Falong a busy A-road, with seemingly
OL,19,Flittle thought of the tragic
OL,20,Fconsequences that could, and sadly
OL,21,Fdid, happen.
OL,26,@pD@MOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777446312
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'talented and
OL,4,Ccreative' woman as drivers jailed over
OL,5,Cher death
OL,7,F"They have both received substantial
OL,8,Fprison sentences and driving
OL,9,Fdisqualifications as a result.
OL,11,F"Our thoughts are with Ella's family,
OL,12,Fwho have been left devastated by what
OL,13,Fhas happened."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
